reviewText: They're great and brand new and came super protected in the box but as you can see its not original disney clamshell atleast not like the original clamshells I have. Its weight is heavy and its a way better quality vhs case then the original but I rather stay as original as i can, i'll be returning this. I removed a star because claiming that its "disney style clamshell" is a bit misleading and considering its not like disney- the price should be lowered. I should've known better though.
